videos.description: QB Justice Hansen finds a wide-open Javonis Issac for a 30-yard touchdown to put Arkansas State on the board.
videos.headline: Arkansas State Hansen connects with Isaac for 30-yard TD

videos.description: Georgia State QB Dan Ellington hits Tamir Jones on the slant, who scores a 36-yard touchdown to even the score at 7-7.
videos.headline: Georgia State's Jones score 26-yard TD

videos.description: Arkansas State's Jonathan Adams beats his man and high points a pass from QB Justice Hansen for a 35-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Hansen launches 35-yard TD pass to Adams

videos.description: Arkansas State RB Marcel Murray spins out of tackle and flies down the sideline for a 64-yard run that sets up the Red Wolves for another touchdown.
videos.headline: Murray spins for 64-yard run

videos.description: Arkansas State's Tajhea Chambers recovers a Georgia State fumble for a 34-yard touchdown to put the Red Wolves up 34-7.
videos.headline: Arkansas State's Chambers scoops and scores 34-yard TD
